page.title: 09HOME LIFE
page.content:
ON{MONDAYS,}AFTER I RISE I CATCH THE BUS TO{SCHOOL.}I WRITE MY NEWS IN THE MORNING, THEN I DO MATHS OR{DOMESDAY } PROJECT. THEN IT IS BREAK. I PLAY DODGE BALL, TIG OR FOOT BALL .SOME TIMES WE PLAY STAR WARS.AFTER BREAK I DO MORE SCHOOL WORK, THEN WE HAVE LUNCH.I PLAY FOR A WHILE THEN IT IS SCHOOL,ENDING AT 3PM.I CATCH THE BUS HOME AND THEN I GO OUT TO PLAY WITH MY FRIENDS.
ON{SATURDAYS,}AFTER RISING I WATCH T.V UNTIL IT IS TIME TO GO SHOPPING.WE SHOP FOR ABOUT 2 HOURS THEN WE GO HOME,WHERE I PRACTISE MY DANCING.AT HALF PAST 1 WE GO TO{DUNDEE {ROYAL INFIRMARY}TO SEE MY BROTHER, WHO WAS IN A ROAD ACCIDENT.WE STAY TILL 5.00 THEN WE LEAVE.WE GO BACK AT SIX TILL EIGHT.I GO TO BED AT TWELVE.
